        <dc:creator><![CDATA[luisherranz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>If the problem is because of yarn, you have to delete your <code>node_modules</code> folder and do <code>npm install</code> instead of <code>yarn</code>.</p>
