      <item>
        <title>No se actualiza</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mburridge]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/xagustin93">@xagustin93</a></p>
<p>We think it’s because you may be using yarn. Try running <code>npx frontity dev</code> or <code>npm run dev</code> instead of <code>yarn dev</code>.</p>
<p>See <a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/support-for-yarn/861" class="inline-onebox">Support for yarn</a></p>
<p>Let me know if that fixes it for you.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/no-se-actualiza/1449/7">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
